United States county-level geographic details

Source: R/us_counties_gazetteer.R
us_county_geo_details.Rd

United States county-level geographic details

us_county_geo_details()

Source

https://raw.githubusercontent.com/josh-byster/fips_lat_long/master/counties.txt

Value

a data frame with county names, FIPS codes, areas, and lat/long

See also

https://www.census.gov/geographies/reference-files/time-series/geo/gazetteer-files.html

Other data-import: beoutbreakprepared_data(), covidtracker_data(), descartes_mobility_data(), healthdata_projections_data(), jhu_data(), jhu_us_data(), kff_icu_beds(), nytimes_county_data(), us_healthcare_capacity(), usa_facts_data()

Examples

usc = us_county_geo_details()
